data.description: 2 ACRES on Corner Wooded Lot. **Hail Resistant Roof 2023** check with your insurance agent it is common for a 30-40% reduction in annual premium. Wonderful ranch style home with 3-4 full beds plus study! Three and a half baths. 1 full bath and 1 flex room up. 2 acres in the Piedmont School District, yet only 3 minutes from Northwest Expressway and Frisco. Northwood Lake Addition is as close to the metro you can get , but still get the privacy you desire. Flexible floor plan , upstairs has an optional room that can easily be a 4th bed and it has a full bath, or use as a 2nd living or media room. Quaint outdoor living with one covered patio and one open flagstone patio. Over sized windows face the wooded greenbelt area through out the entire home. Open living/ dining concept. Kitchen with granite and stainless steel. Over sized 3 car garage with STORM SHELTER. This home has been deep cleaned, carpet and grout  professionally cleaned. This house is truly move in ready. Hail resistant discount roof can help offset these interest rates urge you to check it out!
